Pennzoil Gold SAE 10W-30 Synthetic Blend Motor Oil (CAN) Canada EN 140006579500 EHS V1.0 20-OCT-2022

marketing: Pennzoil^® Gold™ is an advanced synthetic blend formula with Active Cleansing Technology. Utilizes the advantages of blended synthetic technology to better prevent dirt and contaminants from turning into performance robbing deposits. Because at Pennzoil we know, a cleaner engine is better protected and responsive. It meets or exceeds the engine protection required by ILSAC GF-6A and GM dexos1™specifications. It is specially formulated to provide extra protection for severe driving conditions. Formulated for modern engines.
